l7BwM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>艾利什还即将开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-announces-hit-me-hard-and-soft-world-tour-dates-in-uk-north-america-europe-and-australia-3751792">一场盛大的世界巡演，以支持这一纪录</a>，首场巡演将于周日（9 月 29 日）在魁北克举行。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F2257710">此处购买美国门票</a>，此处购买<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F2257710">英国门票</a>，此处购买<a href="https://store.billieeilish.com/pages/tour">欧洲门票</a>，此处购买<a href="https://store.billieeilish.com/pages/tour">澳大利亚门票</a>- 并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-announces-hit-me-hard-and-soft-world-tour-dates-in-uk-north-america-europe-and-australia-3751792">在此处</a>查看完整的日期列表。</p><p>为了准备巡演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-partners-with-google-maps-to-offer-fans-sustainable-transport-to-upcoming-north-american-tour-3796831">这位歌手与谷歌地图合作</a>，帮助粉丝在前往她的演出时找到可持续的交通和食物选择。</p><p>她将与主持人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-keaton">迈克尔·基顿</a>一起担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snl-to-kick-off-50th-season-with-coldplay-stevie-nicks-chappell-roan-and-more-3795032">10 月 19 日<i>《周六夜现场》</i>节目的音乐嘉宾</a>，她最近还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-and-finneas-endorse-kamala-harris-for-president-vote-like-your-life-depends-on-it-because-it-does-3794597">支持卡玛拉·哈里斯参加美国总统竞选</a>。</p><p>本周还有消息称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-is-learning-to-do-home-production-without-finneas-3797325">艾利什现在正在学习“在没有她哥哥芬尼斯的情况下进行家庭制作”</a> ，迄今为止，她的三张专辑都是由芬尼斯制作的。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilis